room_title: Escape room "The Informant" by The Escape • Des Moines in Des Moines
review: Great room. Our group has done a lot of other rooms. By far my favorite. Jamie was great. We will be back

room_title: Escape room "The Informant" by The Escape • Des Moines in Des Moines
review: Saturday was our first time doing anything like this! We had such a great time in The Informant room- and escaped with 1 min 30 sec to spare. Our room host Nate hardly had to give us any hints! He was fantastic :) We are definitely coming back!
